<h2 id="wine">Wine</h2>
<h3 id="grapes">Grapes</h3>
<p>100% Sauvignon Blanc</p>

<h3 id="tasting-notes">Tasting Notes</h3>
<p>Abundant aromas of tropical fruit leap from the glass, white pineapple, ripe passionfruit, mango and guava, and a hint of banana cream pie. The palate is round and open, with accents of ruby red grapefruit, honeysuckle, and melon married with a burst of crisp, refreshing acidity.</p>

