<h3 id="points-of-distinction">Points of Distinction</h3>

<h3 id="food-pairing">Food Pairing</h3>
<p>Noted Bay Area food expert and TV Chef Joanne Weir provided an elegant yet easy recipe for <em>Linguini with Manila Clams and Tomatoes</em> to pair with the 2019 Sauvignon Blanc.</p>

